Heroku Postgres 17 with the New Upgrade Process: Faster Performance, Easier Upgrade (https://hello.heroku.com/e/36622/l-utm-campaign-2506-newsletter/m6ht2g/1309229782/h/eFnn5pPkC-hOxVtVrvfimoN_YJsW57lyxvX_uTh3Mbg)

Postgres 17 is now available on Heroku, bringing faster queries, improved write performance, enhanced JSON support, and better observability, all tuned for modern app workloads. The new upgrade flow uses a single pg:upgrade command with minimal downtime and automatic follower updates, making it easier than ever to stay current. Developers can also take advantage of CLI tools like dryrun, prepare, and wait for flexible and testable upgrade paths.
